<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="opinion-n">opinion <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /ə'pɪnjən/    美 /ə'pɪnjən/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-view">1.★ <strong>[C] 意见；看法；主张 (view)：</strong></h4>
<p>what you think about sb / sth (view)：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>have</strong> / hold <strong>an opinion</strong>
持有看法</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>ask for</strong> / seek <strong>sb’s opinion</strong>
征询某人的意见</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>express / give</strong> / offer / voice <strong>an opinion</strong>
表达主张</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>In my opinion</strong>, learning English is a step-by-step process. 
在我看来，学习英语是一个循序渐进的过程。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I was wondering if you could share your <strong>opinion about / on</strong> this topic.
我想知道您是否能就该话题谈谈您的看法。</p><footer>2017 浙江</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’ve changed my <strong>opinion of</strong> her.
我改变了对她的看法。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-u">2.★ <strong>[U] (群体的) 观点；舆论：</strong></h4>
<p>what people in general think about sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>legal / medical opinion
法律/医学界的观点</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>Public opinion</strong> is in favour of change.
公众舆论支持改革。</p></div>

<h4 id="3-c">3.★ <strong>[C] 专家意见；专业意见：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>get a lawyer’s <strong>opinion on</strong> the question
请教律师对这个问题的意见</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’d like a <strong>second opinion</strong> (= advice from another person) before I make a decision.
在作决定前我想再听听别人的意见。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="have-a-high-low-good-poor-opinion-of">have a high / low / good / poor opinion of</h3>
<p>1.<strong>对…评价高 / 低 / 好 / 差</strong>  </p></div>